{"tid":657044,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"《Arsène Wenger》(原曲：最佳損友 - 陳奕迅)","createTime":"2018-05-07T18:22:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T19:56:23.000Z","uid":112702,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c66bff4f64bc795bf9ba0ffbe2aeaab77894f272","tid":657044,"uid":112702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T18:22:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SpVC2ZBrwBQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSpVC2ZBrwBQ&d=ltR1ESwHDkZv1QxYodHvaZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=54274592\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SpVC2ZBrwBQ</a><br />\n<br />\n雲格　過去你可有時間　能夠印證你一切評價<br />\n無悔　意興卻消失難返　而你才能仍是無價<br />\n<br />\n雲格　每季也失去籌碼　前四卻靠你得到資格<br />\n球賽　每次進攻都如畫<br />\n始終留戀　過去你的改革<br />\n<br />\n由來甚遠　當初一早展出規管天賦<br />\n更會對世界去向預計<br />\n精於分析隊中小子優勢　於比賽裡發揮<br />\n食材同時還限制<br />\n<br />\n但是任內並未計算派系<br />\n不得不放棄　遠去日本<br />\n並在季度裡　塑造了近況未來<br />\n甚至決賽　戰勝勁旅<br />\n<br />\n大概計劃裡　你沒有在意<br />\n將是一項的歷史<br />\n當日稱是誰　來年便想起　<br />\n在記錄會找到證據<br />\n<br />\n英超歲月裡是你　破壞了局勢<br />\n讓寶座可不用總是誰<br />\n成為第一位　外國藉　對獎杯佔據<br />\n<br />\n輾轉之間將軍隊都升格<br />\n每個賽季裡抗拒後退<br />\n開始修補雙方一絲差距<br />\n終於再次領獎　讓球迷尋樂趣<br />\n<br />\n大量任用外地各個勇士<br />\n掀起的變革　再創歷史<br />\n就是季度裡　你讓挫敗缺席時<br />\n讓這世界　獻上謝意<br />\n<br />\n在你決定要創立這盛世<br />\n爭奪多項的目標<br />\n可是新浪潮　能憑著資金在照耀　更改寫撮要<br />\n<br />\n股東卻在說著要擴大這位置<br />\n用新地址　將敵方動搖<br />\n球場下資金　就這樣變得可笑了<br />\n<br />\n當初的你付上力氣訓練了未來<br />\n全部來日卻賣了　以敵對自居<br />\n你亦能在有限裡　以第四站台<br />\n輿論卻是說　應分開<br />\n<br />\n歲月裡　獻盡了父愛<br />\n一直忍受不避開<br />\n只是想未來　重回舊精彩<br />\n像昨日　冠軍總滿載<br />\n<br />\n可惜世代變換了　價值缺乏了<br />\n被逼敗走　失落的下台<br />\n無能力執手　讓故事再添加記載<br />\n都始終答謝　往日你奉獻沒計較過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCredit to DC （改詞）, 柒菇碌叔叔（演唱）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想念雲爺爺了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ffcea871ff5a5a5c72c84612efdb1b39eb62bc2","tid":657044,"uid":16320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T18:32:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beea089e3b295d3539c2900edc9443a7634b740b","tid":657044,"uid":77880,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T18:39:59.000Z","msg":"D 音唔太岩"},{"pid":"f640538b8fd66e45e8c66ef8d5d8e77ff88d94bc","tid":657044,"uid":10608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T18:50:13.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"9e32235f6a1a9b9736cdfd7e9ac526a65ba678c3","tid":657044,"uid":72990,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T18:51:52.000Z","msg":"屌又係教友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a8bc17a947f750e19fbc6601390d2d5ee157c9","tid":657044,"uid":17522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T18:56:28.000Z","msg":"呢首啲詞有幾下好似唔啱音<br />\n<br />\n但整體嚟講好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講哂雲加成個生涯 帶到最後個種遺憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fcce2e68c4ea1ce328443c461f975c6721950ca","tid":657044,"uid":26003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T19:56:23.000Z","msg":"雲爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}